{"id": "1523297624990683147", "channel_id": "1523297624990683147", "author_id": "1481778833752592436", "author_name": "nanami_carocontrolmeta", "content": "This proposal focuses on introducing unlockable skill kits and card deck variants for existing characters rather than fully reworking them. By tying these new kits to specific milestones like reaching 100 points in wave modes or earning event exchange items, players get a rewarding way to dust off their older rosters and experiment with fresh builds. This approach gives veteran players a meaningful reason to keep using their characters during content droughts, while offering newer players the flexibility to customize their playstyle using saved resources, all while keeping the core identity of each character completely intact. As shown in the attached examples, these are not balance reworks or overhauls, but rather optional, unlockable kit choices that players can activate to change how a character plays.", "timestamp": "2026-07-05T12:00:55.299000+00:00", "thread_id": "1523297624990683147", "edited_timestamp": "2026-07-05T17:24:30.911000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "Saya_wow", "emoji_id": "1513124172895879198", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "What", "emoji_id": "1356085150869622965", "count": 8}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1523297625691127989", "filename": "Idea_A1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1838269, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1523297624990683147/1523297625691127989/Idea_A1.png?ex=6a4b98f7&is=6a4a4777&hm=6bbeea9f304a30529dba98a226cbea94d6ea594c0d7d0d957b977e976201420c&"}, {"id": "1523297626395508756", "filename": "Idea_A2.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1826691, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1523297624990683147/1523297626395508756/Idea_A2.png?ex=6a4b98f7&is=6a4a4777&hm=7d095de1ca16d977d7dd1ed4b66e1a2d1df82617e79e651146df25898f9f45a4&"}]}
